          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1576.-step-7-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1576.-step-7-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Cut the<strong> warmed pitta</strong> into triangles</p><p>Serve the <strong>lamb kofte</strong> with the <strong>tabbouleh</strong>, <strong>pitta</strong> and <strong>tzatziki</strong> to the side</p><p>Garnish with a<strong> lemon wedge</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
      "order": 8,
